Quote:  ... . advocacy of half-way homes for persons suffering from psychiatric disorders. Many patients entering our mental hospitals today are voluntary boarders and, as such are in possession of their powers of reasoning ... they may be put in wards with patients suffering from all types of mental disorders. Half-way homes could overcome this problem by being used for these people ...
